The '''Mezzicanley Wave''' was the fourth [[Wikipedia:state of matter|state of matter]], caused when crystalline solids reached temperatures near or at absolute zero. It was a volatile state that would cause whatever achieved it to explode into numerous shards.

In [[25 ABY/Legends|25 ABY]], during the [[Battle of Helska IV]], the ice-world [[Helska IV]] was destroyed by using [[Shieldship]]s to cause it to reach the Mezzicanley Wave.

